Syntax: headbutt <target>

Delivers a headbutt to an opponent, striking with the forehead or helm.
Headbutt is a Warrior-line combat skill handled by the Warrior attack
system. It is available to Warden-class characters and their remort
descendants (Knight, Swordsman, Crusader).

The attack can potentially disrupt the target's combat rhythm and deals
physical damage.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp headbutt bash smash knee charge
